# Journey harness transient per-journey records (aggregated into journey-results.json)
apps/dentalemon/.journey-tmp/
# Journey harness aggregate report — a generated, environment-specific artifact
# (ceph journeys SKIP without MinIO). Nothing reads the committed copy; CI
# regenerates it each run and uploads it as an artifact. Keep it out of VCS.
apps/dentalemon/journey-results.json
# Stability-budget aggregate report — generated by run-stability-budget.ts when
# banking the harness N×. CI regenerates + uploads it as an artifact.
apps/dentalemon/stability-budget-results.json

# Auto-generated requirements-traceability matrix (regenerated by `bun run
# audit:trace` from BR/AC tags in tests). Regenerable + churns as coverage
# changes, and no CI job regenerates it — a committed copy would rot. The
# generator path is documented in docs/prd/BUSINESS_RULES.md. Keep it out of VCS.
docs/testing/TRACEABILITY_MATRIX_AUTO.md

